No. 128,

Orig.

Alaska v. United States.

Motion of the Special Master for fees and reimbursement of expenses granted, and the Special Master is awarded a total of $12,963.14 for the period October 16, 2000, through April 16, 2001, to be paid equally by the parties. [For earlier order herein, see, e. g., ante, p. 1006.]
